===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To [[communicate]] to someone else by means of [[voice]].
# To [[communicate]] to someone else by means other than [[speech]].

====Etymology====
From Middle English [[talken]], from Swedish [[tolka]], Danish [[tolke]], or Icelandic [[túlka]], (interpret, explain), which are derivatives of Swedish and Danish [[tolk]], Icelandic [[túlkr]], respectively, all from Lithuanian [[tulkas]] (an interpreter)

